{"tid":2126827,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點解冇人講呢條片？「三峽潰壩預演」","createTime":"2020-07-27T05:08:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T05:39:11.000Z","uid":326881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ca0f3918bfd501b0975f243fcf2c757789edc437","tid":2126827,"uid":326881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T05:08:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZEEweAJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZEEweAJ.png&h=441e0ebd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4r8d13VI2mc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4r8d13VI2mc&d=EOe11knUQePtQJIakN8qx9xiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=1ffb1bcc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4r8d13VI2mc</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"orange\">呢條片係講緊長江中下游非汛期*發生<span class=\"red\">三山夹大土贝</span>潰壩既模擬，而家大陸水浸到第三號洪峰，受災程度肯定比呢個模擬結果嚴重得多。呢個時候內地UP條咁既片上網「擾亂民心」，係咪代表共產黨內部派系鬥爭、意見分歧越來越大？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">*<span class=\"orange\">汛期</span>：蝗語中為「水位明顯上升的時期/水漲期」的意思。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\">以下內容節錄自Yahoo新聞：<br />\n網傳三峽潰壩模擬影片 下洩洪水將以時速70公里摧毀宜昌<br />\n<br />\n影片指出，三峽大壩高度達181米，壩體長度2.3公里，正常蓄水高度175米，總容量393億立方米；影片模擬壩體完全粉碎，指下洩的洪水在迅速摧毀宜昌市後，將以不低於時速60公里的速度淹沒沿途城鎮，洪水高度約15至20米，並在淹沒宜都後會以扇形前進，受災面積將大增，洪水除沿主河道摧毀荊州，擴散出去的洪水將直奔武漢。<br />\n<br />\n一名安徽省防汛人員觀看影片後，認為該片應該是半官方機構做出的沙盤推演，他認為一般人無法做出如此專業的推測；<span class=\"orange\">而為何該片會在網上流傳，可能是當局有相關的目的，或許目前三峽大壩已經有問題浮現</span>；他又表示，若再發生超大暴雨的話，會使防汛形勢更為嚴峻，三峽大壩上游一旦再有超大洪水，情況將相當危險。</span>"},{"pid":"337387c67c95b18517ad13427bc011b0c5f87b66","tid":2126827,"uid":191667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T05:09:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"12a032a046d185874b484e76484a2e6f7ea7b4da","tid":2126827,"uid":266654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T05:10:50.000Z","msg":"是撚旦啦<br />\n唔係以為冚家產完，支那種會反抗?<br />\n自己攞黎唔怪得人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458b90b485fef91b2d97c85eeb67724607ef9d8d","tid":2126827,"uid":37874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T05:13:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ef04869c0b006ebb5aef243b6fa625167779b3","tid":2126827,"uid":31320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T05:17:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jTJEoAA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjTJEoAA.jpg&h=b31edc7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1257bf0de660956403b9bb51ccb5fdc8f9e9a9e1","tid":2126827,"uid":364053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T05:39:11.000Z","msg":"好痴線。。。"}]}